# URL patterns skipped by lychee (the markdown link check in .github/workflows/pre_test.yml).
# CI runs lychee with --offline, which already skips every remote URL; the patterns
# below are defensive so a local `lychee "**/*.md"` without --offline stays quiet on
# loopback addresses and placeholder domains that are never expected to resolve.
https?://localhost
https?://127\.0\.0\.1
https?://0\.0\.0\.0
https?://host\.docker\.internal
https?://([a-z0-9-]+\.)*example\.(com|org|net)
